    • choice

      public ItemField<E> choice(String backPointerName)
      Causes this ItemField to create a choice constraint.

      This ItemField becomes the target of the copy constraint. The field pointing back becomes the template, and Type.getThis() of the type of this ItemField becomes the copy.

      Parameters:
      backPointerName - the name of the field pointing back; at E, this has to be the name of an ItemField where the value type overlaps with this item field's Feature.getType()
